<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="marriage-n">marriage <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mærɪdʒ/    美 /'mærɪdʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp;[U] 结婚；婚姻：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>happy marriage</strong> 
幸福的婚姻</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Their marriage lasted 31 years. 
他们的婚姻持续了31年。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-c-wedding">2.★ <strong>[C] 结婚仪式；婚礼 (wedding)</strong></h4>
<h4 id="3c">3.<strong>[C] 密切结合：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the perfect marriage of rice and milk
米糊和牛奶的完美融合</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Charles Dresser performed their<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (marry) ceremony in 1824.  （2021浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. marriage  </p></div>